<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently the minHeight property of the Zend_Dojo_Form_Element_Editor can only be set to em, whereas the height property can be set to em, px or %.</p>

<p>It would be nice to be able to set the minHeight with em, px or %.</p>

